author: WCAX News
title: Police search for missing Fair Haven teen
text:
FAIR HAVEN, Vt. - Police are searching for a missing Fair Haven teen.
Authorities say Isaac Voisine, 13, was last seen on Adams Street around 10 p.m. Monday.
Voisine is about 5-feet-8-inches tall, 155 pounds, with short brown hair and brown eyes. He was last seen wearing blue jeans, black sneakers and carrying a black backpack.
Police would like to hear from anyone who has seen Voisine. Call Fair Haven police at 802-265-8293.
